      "quick_assessment": "Qiimayn degdeg ah.",
      "daily_routine_templates": "⏱ Qaababka nidaamka maalinlaha",
      "pre_built_sequences_of_activities_that": "Taxanayaal hawlood oo horay loo dhisay oo ku habboon xannibaadaha waqtiga caadiga (10 daqiiqo, 30 daqiiqo, 45 daqiiqo). Dooro mid oo raac.",
