      "generate_a_3_question_exit_ticket_on_t": "Abuur tigidh bixitaan 3-su'aal ah mowduuca hadda la baray. Daabac oo bixi dhammaadka casharka.",
      "topic_2": "Mowduuc",
      "generate_and_print_exit_ticket": "🖨 Abuur oo daabac tigidhka bixitaanka",
      "grade_3_fraction_assessment_checklist": "Liiska Hubinta Qiimaynta Qeybta Fasalka 3",
      "grade_4_fraction_assessment_checklist": "Liiska Hubinta Qiimaynta Qeybta Fasalka 4",
      "grade_5_fraction_assessment_checklist": "Liiska Hubinta Qiimaynta Qeybta Fasalka 5",
      "assessment_checklist": "☑ Liiska hubinta qiimaynta",
      "per_grade_skills_checklists_use_during": "Liisas hubin xirfad oo fasal kasta. Isticmaal inta lagu jiro qiimayn qof-qof ah ama si aad u qorsheyso waxbarida.",
      "my_child_says_i_hate_fractions": "Ilmahaygu wuxuu leeyahay \"Waan necbahay qeybaha\"",
      "very_common_fractions_break_the_rules_": "Aad bay u caansan tahay. Qeybuhu waxay jebiyaan xeerarka ardaydu ku barato tirooyinka dhan — tirooyinka waaweyn had iyo jeer macnaheedu ma aha qiimayaal waaweyn. Xanaaqu waa dhab iyo caadi. Ka caawi: (1) adigoo isticmaalaya qaabab muuqaal ah sida pizza ama xariiqyada qeybta, (2) adigoo ku xiraya nolosha dhabta (karinta, waqtiga, lacagta), (3) adigoo ku celceliya wax yar oo joogto (5 daqiiqo maalintii) halkii fadhi dheer, (4) adigoo ammaanaya dadaalka, ma aha kaliya jawaabaha saxda.",
      "my_child_doesn_t_understand_why_proced": "Ilmahaygu ma fahmo SABABTA nidaamyadu u shaqeeyaan",
      "they_are_not_alone_most_students_learn": "Kaligood ma aha — ardayda badankood waxay bartaan nidaamka marka hore, sababta na dib. Ka caawi adigoo had iyo jeer muujinaya sida nidaamku u eg yahay sawir. \"Isku dhufo 3/4 iyo 1/2\" waxaa loo sawiri karaa afargeeso. Tabka Op Proofs ayaa taas kuu sameeya. Weyddii \"maxay?\" si tartiib iyo mar walba.",
      "my_child_gets_the_procedure_right_but_": "Ilmahaygu wuxuu saxaa nidaamka laakiin jawaabtu waa khaldan",
      "usually_means_a_small_arithmetic_error": "Badanaa waxay ka dhigan tahay qalad xisaabeed yar (tusaale, isku dhuftay khalad) ama ma fududayn. Tus Cheat Sheet — waxay hubin karaan shaqadooda tallaabo tallaabo. Ku dhiirrigeli inay ku xaqiijiyaan hab kale (marka hore qiyaas, ama isticmaal qaab kale).",
      "what_if_i_don_t_remember_fractions_wel": "Ka warran haddii aan anigu si fiican u xasuusan qeybaha?",
      "you_don_t_have_to_be_the_expert_use_th": "Uma baahnid inaad khabiir noqoto! Isticmaal Tab Guide iyo Worked Examples — waxay si cad u sharraxaan nidaamyada. Ka fiican: tus \"aan wada ogaano tan.\" Waad la baran kartaa ilmahaaga. Tabka Vocabulary wuu faa'iido leeyahay xitaa dadka waaweyn.",
      "how_do_i_know_if_my_child_is_on_track": "Sideen u ogaan karaa haddii ilmahaygu jidka saaran yahay?",
      "look_at_the_standards_tab_to_see_which": "Eeg tabka Standards si aad u aragto heerarka CCSS ee ay tahay inay ogaadaan fasalkooda. Tabka Mastery wuxuu muujiyaa horumarka. Hubin degdeg ah: ma sawiri karaan (a) qaab 3/4, (b) sheegi karaan qeyb la mid ah 1/2, (c) isbarbardhigi karaan 2/3 iyo 3/4 oo sharraxi karaan? Saddexdaas tijaabo waxay daboolaan filashooyinka qeybta K-5 badankooda.",
      "parent_guide": "👨‍👩‍👧 Hagaha waalidka",
      "guidance_for_parents_helping_kids_with": "Hagitaan waalidiinta caawinaya carruurta qeybaha guriga. Caqabadaha caadiga, talooyin la taaban karo, iyo waxa la weyddiiyo.",
      "the_why_of_learning_recruiting_interes": "\"SABABTA\" waxbarashada — soo-jiidashada xiisaha, joogtaynta dadaalka, is-xakameynta",
      "the_what_of_learning_perception_langua": "\"WAXA\" waxbarashada — aragti, luqad, faham",
      "the_how_of_learning_physical_action_ex": "\"SIDA\" waxbarashada — ficil jireed, muujin, hawl fulineed",
      "udl_alignment_cast_guidelines": "🎨 Isku-dubbaridka UDL — tilmaamaha CAST",
      "every_fraction_lab_feature_mapped_to_a": "Astaan kasta oo Fraction Lab ah oo lagu xiray tilmaanta Universal Design for Learning (UDL) ee CAST. ",
      "use_this_to_articulate_to_administrato": "Isticmaal tan si aad ugu sharraxdo maamulayaasha ama dib-u-eegayaasha deeqda sida AlloFlow u hawlgeliyo UDL.",
      "feature": "Astaan",
      "udl_principle": "Mabda'a UDL",
      "the_foundational_ies_practice_guide_5_": "IES Practice Guide aasaasiga. 5 talooyin oo ay ku jirto isticmaalka dhexe ee qaabka xariiqda-tirada.",
      "origin_of_the_enactive_concrete_iconic": "Asalka horumarka enactive (taabasho) → iconic (matalaad) → symbolic (aan la taaban karin) ee noqda CRA.",
