      "research_citations": "📚 Tixraacyada cilmi-baarista",
      "the_research_base_for_alloflow_fractio": "Aasaaska cilmi-baarista ee AlloFlow Fraction Lab. Isticmaal tixraacyadan marka aad caddaynayso isticmaalka qalabka maamulayaasha, diiwaanka IEP, ama codsiyada deeqaha.",
