      "a_5_chapter_story_where_each_chapter_i": "Sheeko 5-cutub oo cutub kastaa uu yahay dhibaato qeyb oo macne leh. Ka shaqee maalinta roodhi-samaynta si aad u dabaqdo xirfadahaaga.",
