      "a_short_daily_ritual_5_problems_per_da": "Cibaado maalinle gaaban: 5 dhibaatood maalintii. Dhis taxane. Jadwalka celcelinta waxay ka adkaataa xoogga celcelinta haynta.",
      "practice_streak": "Taxanaha celcelinta",
      "mark_today_complete": "✓ Calaamadee maanta oo dhammaystiran",
      "today_done_come_back_tomorrow": "✓ Maanta waa dhammaatay! Berri soo noqo.",
      "last_14_days": "14kii maalmood ee la soo dhaafay:",
      "the_1_2_trick": "Xeeladda 1/2",
      "let_your_number_be_n_the_sequence_n_1_": "Ha tiradaadu ahaato n. Taxanaha: (n+1) × 2 + 4 − 6 = 2n + 2 + 4 − 6 = 2n. Qeybi 2 → n. Ka jar asalka → 0. Sug — taasi waxay siisaa 0, ma aha 1. Isku day: n → (n+1)×2 = 2n+2 → +4 = 2n+6 → −6 = 2n → ÷2 = n → −asalka = 0. \"Xeeladdu\" waxay ku tiirsan tahay constants qarsoon oo taxanaha ku jira.",
      "sum_of_unit_fractions": "Wadarta qeybaha halbeeg",
      "each_term_is_half_the_previous_the_tot": "Eray kastaa waa badh kii hore. Wadartu waxay u dhowaataa 1 laakiin weligeed ma gaadho. Kani waa taxane geometric aan dhammaad lahayn oo leh eray kowaad 1/2 iyo saami 1/2: S = (1/2) / (1 − 1/2) = 1. Taas awgeed paradox-ka dhaqdhaqaaqa ee Zeno xisaab ahaan loo xallin karaa.",
      "the_harmonic_series": "Taxanaha harmonic",
      "even_though_each_term_is_small_the_ser": "In kastoo eray kastaa yar yahay, taxanahu wuu kala firdhaa. Si aad u gaadho 100, waxaad u baahan tahay qiyaastii 1.5 × 10^43 eray. Tan waxaa caddeeyay Nicole Oresme 1300meeyadii isticmaalka kooxaynta: 1/3 + 1/4 > 1/4 + 1/4 = 1/2; 1/5+...+1/8 > 4 × 1/8 = 1/2; had iyo jeer waad heli kartaa 1/2 kale oo aad ku darto.",
      "farey_sequences": "Taxanayaasha Farey",
      "check_1_4_and_1_3_4_1_1_3_1_check_2_5_": "Hubi 1/4 iyo 1/3: (4)(1) − (1)(3) = 1. Hubi 2/5 iyo 1/2: (5)(1) − (2)(2) = 1. Sifadan waxay abuurtaa geedka Stern-Brocot ee dhammaan tirooyinka macquulka.",
      "multiplying_telescopes": "Telescopes isku-dhufan",
      "rewrite_1_2_2_3_3_4_n_1_n_the_2_in_2_3": "Dib u qor: 1/2 × 2/3 × 3/4 × ... × (n−1)/n. 2da ku jirta 2/3 waxay tirtirtaa 2da ku jirta tirada hoosta ee 1/2. 3da ku jirta 3/4 waxay tirtirtaa 3da ku jirta tirada hoosta ee 2/3. Wax kastaa waa la tirtiraa marka laga reebo 1/n.",
      "fraction_magic_tricks": "🎩 Xeeladaha sixirka qeybta",
      "mathematical_tricks_that_are_really_el": "\"Xeelado\" xisaabeed oo dhab ahaantii ah aqoonsiyo qeyb oo qurux badan. Dooro mid si aad u aragto dejinta, muujinta, iyo sharraxaadda xisaabeed.",
      "setup": "🎬 Dejin",
      "reveal": "✨ Muujin",
      "why_does_this_work": "🧠 Maxay tani u shaqaysaa?",
      "ruler_inches": "Mastar (inch)",
      "a_standard_inch_ruler_is_divided_into_": "Mastar inch caadi waxaa loo qeybiyaa lix-iyo-toban meelood. Xariiqyada waaweyn: inch. Calaamadda badhka: 1/2 inch. Calaamadda rubuca: 1/4 inch. Qeybta ugu yar: 1/16 inch.",
      "1_1_16_or_1_0625": "1 1/16 (ama 1.0625)",
      "inch_rulers_use_binary_fractions_halve": "Mastarrada inch waxay isticmaalaan qeybo binary: badhabo, rubuc, sideed-meelood, lix-iyo-toban-meelood.",
      "tape_measure_carpentry": "Cabbir shariidh (nijaarnimo)",
      "a_12_foot_tape_measure_has_marks_every": "Cabbir shariidh 12-cagood wuxuu leeyahay calaamado 1/16 inch kasta. Isticmaal caadi: akhri ilaa 1/8 ama 1/16 ugu dhow. Dheeman madow 19 3/16 inch kasta waxay calaamadeeyaan kala-fogaanta joist ee la naqshadeeyay.",
      "5_19_3_16_95_15_16_inches_8_feet": "5 × 19 3/16 = 95 15/16 inch ≈ 8 cagood",
      "each_16_inches_has_a_black_diamond_for": "16 inch kasta waxay leeyihiin dheeman madow oo kala-fogaanta stud caadiga.",
      "measuring_cups": "Koobabka cabbirka",
      "a_standard_set_includes_1_cup_1_2_1_3_": "Set caadi wuxuu ku jiraa 1 koob, 1/2, 1/3, 1/4. Setyada qaar waxay ku daraan 2/3 iyo 3/4. Koobabka cabbirka galaaska waxay leeyihiin calaamado 1/4, 1/3, 1/2, 2/3, 3/4 koob iyo 1 koob.",
      "1_4_1_2_3_4_use_both_or_three_1_4_cup_": "1/4 + 1/2 = 3/4 (isticmaal labada, AMA saddex 1/4 koob)",
