      "barry_harris_1929_2021_codified_bebop_": "Barry Harris (1929-2021) wo habeeyay harmony-ga bebop. Nidaamkiisu wo isticmaalaa 6th chords halkii 7ths, wuxuuna ku daraa diminished passing chords inta u dhaxaysa darajooyinka scale si loo hago codka si siman.",
      "ii_v_i_jazz": "ii-V-I (Jazz)",
