      "7th_overtone": "Overtone 7aad",
      "attack_time_to_reach_full_volume_decay": "Attack: wakhtiga la gaaro volume-ka buuxa. Decay: wakhtiga la hoos u dhaco sustain. Sustain: heerka volume-ka la hayo. Release: wakhtiga uu ka baabbo'o kadib marka key la sii daayo.",
      "a_scale_is_an_ordered_set_of_pitches_m": "Scale wa ururka pitches oo la habeeyay. Modes wa wareega scale oo ka bilaabma darajooyin kala duwan. Mid kastaa wo abuuraa dareen shucuureed oo kala duwan.",
      "chords_are_built_by_stacking_intervals": "Chords waxaa la dhisaa iyadoo la kaydsanayo intervals (3rds). Major wo isticmaalaa major 3rd + minor 3rd. Minor wuu rogaa. Extended chords wo ku daraan 7ths, 9ths, iyo wixii ka badan.",
      "kicks_use_a_sine_oscillator_with_a_pit": "Kicks wo isticmaalaan sine oscillator oo leh pitch sweep. Snares wo isku daraan noise (la sifeeyay) + tone body. Hi-hats wo isticmaalaan high-pass filtered noise bursts.",
      "4_4_4_quarter_note_beats_per_bar_most_": "4/4 = 4 quarter-note beats bar kasta (kan ugu badan). 3/4 = dareenka waltz. 6/8 = compound duple. 5/4 iyo 7/8 wo abuuraan grooves aan sinnayn, ajanabi ah.",
      "keys_arranged_by_ascending_5ths_clockw": "Keys waxaa loo habeeyay 5ths koor u kaca oo saacad-raac ah. Keys deriska ah wo wadaagaan 6 ka mid ah 7 notes. U socodka saacad-raac wo ku daraa sharps; lidka saacadda wo ku daraa flats.",
      "every_musical_sound_contains_overtones": "Cod kasta oo muusiko ah wo ka kooban yahay overtones ka sarreeya fundamental. Xooggooda isku xiran ayaa go'aamiya timbre — sababtaas ayaa turumbo uga duwan yahay flute pitch isku mid ah.",
      "an_interval_is_the_distance_between_tw": "Interval wa masaafada u dhaxaysa laba pitches, oo lagu cabbiro semitones. Frequency ratio ayaa go'aamiya consonance (ratios fudud sida 3:2 way jilicsan yihiin).",
      "plays_chord_notes_one_at_a_time_in_seq": "Wo ciyaartaa notes chord mid mid isku xigxig. Koor = hoos ilaa koor, Hoos = koor ilaa hoos. Wo abuurtaa patterns socda oo ka yimaada chords taagan.",
      "a_filter_removes_frequencies_above_low": "Filter wo saaraa frequencies ka sarreeya (lowpass), ka hooseeya (highpass), ama agagaarka (bandpass) cutoff frequency. Resonance (Q) wo kordhiyaa frequencies u dhow cutoff, isagoo abuuraya peak.",
      "tremolo_periodic_volume_changes_amplit": "Tremolo: isbeddel volume xilliyeed (amplitude modulation). Vibrato: isbeddel pitch xilliyeed (frequency modulation). Labadaba wo maamula LFO (Low Frequency Oscillator).",
      "discovered_in_1983_a_noise_burst_feeds": "Waxaa la ogaaday 1983. Noise burst wo galaa delay line aad u gaaban oo feedback leh. Delay time ayaa go'aamiya pitch. Filter ku jira feedback loop wo maamulaa iftiinka iyo decay. Wo si dabiici ah u ku ekaadaa plucked strings.",
      "the_sequencer_is_a_composition_tool_ea": "Sequencer wa qalab curinta. Step kasta wo matalaa subdivision beat. Safka melody wo dejiyaa pitched notes, drums wo ku daraan rhythm. Musical notation wo muujiyaa waxaad abuurto.",
      "notes_on_lines_and_spaces_represent_pi": "Notes ku yaal xariiqyada iyo meelaha bannaan wo matalaan pitches. Muddada wo muujiya qaabka note: whole (○), half (𝅗𝅥), quarter (♩), eighth (♪). Staff wo leeyahay 5 xariiq.",
