      "equal_temperament_12_notes_per_octave_": "Equal temperament: 12 notes octave kasta, ratio 2^(1/12). A4 = 440 Hz; A5 = 880 Hz. Well-Tempered Clavier ee Bach (1722) ayaa adduunka ku qanciyay heshiiskan. Note kasta oo aad halkan ciyaartid wo ku yaal grid-kaas.",
      "scales_the_major_minor_modal_grammar": "Scales — naxwaha major + minor + modal",
      "major_w_w_h_w_w_w_h_minor_w_h_w_w_h_w_": "Major: W-W-H-W-W-W-H. Minor: W-H-W-W-H-W-W. 7-da modes (Ionian, Dorian, Phrygian, Lydian, Mixolydian, Aeolian, Locrian) wo ka yimaadaan wareejinta interval pattern ee major scale.",
      "chords_stacked_thirds_inversions": "Chords — stacked thirds + inversions",
      "triads_root_third_fifth_major_4_3_semi": "Triads: root + third + fifth. Major (4+3 semitones), minor (3+4), diminished (3+3), augmented (4+4). 7th chords wo ku daraan third kale. Muusikada pop = ~6 chords oo ku celcelinaya; jazz wo isticmaalaa extensions iyo substitutions.",
      "harmony_pad_voiced_pads_drones": "Harmony Pad — voiced pads + drones",
      "sustained_chord_textures_the_bed_under": "Sustained chord textures — sariirta ka hooseysa ku dhawaad cinematic score kasta. Isku day iv-V-i minor, ama i-VI-VII dareenka Hans Zimmer. Drones fifths wo taageeraan muusikada classical Hindiya iyo dhaqamada bagpipe.",
      "beat_pad_sample_based_drums": "Beat Pad — sample-based drums",
      "most_popular_music_sits_at_4_4_90_130_": "Muusikada caanka ah badankeed wo ku jirtaa 4/4, 90-130 BPM. Hip-hop ~85-95, house 120-130, drum-and-bass ~170 (dareenka half-time). Kick 1+3, snare 2+4 = backbeat — aasaaska rock + pop.",
      "theory_the_math_behind_the_sound": "Theory — xisaabta ka danbeysa codka",
      "pythagoras_500_bce_discovered_consonan": "Pythagoras (~500 BCE) wo ka helay consonance integer frequency ratios: octave 2:1, fifth 3:2, fourth 4:3. Helmholtz wuu balaadhiyay 1862. Cod = compression waves; muusiko = patterns aan ku heshiinnay inaan ku magacowno quruxsan.",
