      "fm_synthesis_2": "FM Synthesis",
      "frequency_modulation_fm_synthesis_uses": "Frequency Modulation (FM) synthesis wo isticmaalaa hal oscillator (modulator) si degdeg ah u bedelo frequency-ga mid kale (carrier). Ratio modulator:carrier ayaa go'aamiya harmonic content. Ratios fudud (1:1, 2:1, 3:1) wo soo saaraan harmonic tones. Ratios adag wo soo saaraan metallic, bell-like, ama inharmonic sounds. Yamaha DX7 ayaa FM caan ka dhigay 1983.",
