      "supersaw_stacks_multiple_sawtooth_osci": "SuperSaw wo isku kaydiyaa sawtooth oscillators badan oo si yar loo detune-gareeyay midba midka kale. Tani wo abuurtaa cod weyn, ballaadhan, dhalaalaya — calaamada EDM, trance, iyo pop casri ah. Voices badan = ka qaro weyn laakiin isticmaala CPU badan. Detuning wo maamulaa inta ay voices ka fog yihiin tuning-ka — detune badan = ballaadhan/sida chorus badan, yar = adag/diiraddan.",
