      "arpeggiator_gate": "Gate ee arpeggiator",
      "an_arpeggiator_plays_the_notes_of_a_ch": "🔬 Arpeggiator wo ciyaaraa notes chord mid mid isku xigxig. \"Koor\" wo u socdaa hoos ilaa koor, isagoo abuuraya tamar koor u kacaysa. \"Hoos\" wuu hoos u dhacaa dareenka biyo-dhac. Xawaaraha wo maamulaa xawaaraha (yar = degdeg). Gate wo maamulaa inta ay note kasta dhawaaqdo (100% = legato, 10% = staccato). Isku day xawaare=100ms + 4 octaves + up pattern classic trance arp!",
      "live_mic_effects_lab": "🎤 Live Mic Effects Lab",
