      "removes_frequencies_above_lowpass_or_b": "Wo saaraa frequencies ka sarreeya (lowpass) ama ka hooseeya (highpass) threshold. Sida gacan lagu daboolo afka — frequencies sarreeya way baabba'aan, codku wo noqdaa mid \"madoow\" oo dheeraad ah.",
      "delay": "Delay",
      "creates_echoes_by_copying_the_signal_a": "Wo abuuraa dhawaaqyo iyadoo la koobbiyayo signal-ka oo dib loo ciyaaro muddo gaaban ka dib. Feedback wo maamulaa tirada dhawaaqyada dib u soo noqda.",
      "reverb_2": "Reverb",
      "simulates_room_acoustics_by_creating_t": "Wo ku ekaadaa acoustics-ka qol iyadoo la abuurayo kumanaan dhawaaq yaryar oo isku dhex jira. Qol yar = reverb gaaban, kaniisad weyn = reverb dheer.",
      "distortion": "Distortion",
      "clips_the_waveform_peaks_turning_smoot": "Wo jaraa waveform peaks, isagoo u rogaya sine waves jilicsan qaabab adag, geesood leh. Tani wo ku dartaa harmonics cusub oo aan ku jirin codka asalka ah.",
      "chorus": "Chorus",
      "duplicates_the_signal_with_a_slight_co": "Wo koobbiyaa signal-ka delay yar oo si joogto ah u bedelaya. Tani wo ku ekaataa voices/aalado badan oo isku ciyaaraya iyagoo aan si buuxda isu waafaqsanayn.",
      "tremolo": "Tremolo",
      "rapidly_varies_the_volume_up_and_down_": "Wo si degdeg ah u bedelaa volume-ka koor iyo hoos, isagoo abuuraya saameyn garaacaya. Wa caan guitar-ka surf iyo muusikada organ.",
      "use_headphones_when_monitoring_to_avoi": "Isticmaal headphones marka aad monitor-gareyneyso si aad uga fogaato feedback loops! Mic-ku wo maraa dhammaan effects-ka kore (filter, delay, reverb, iwm.) — hagaaji si aad u maqasho sida mid kastaa u beddelo codkaaga ama aaladdaada.",
