      "eccentricity_0_05_essentially_circular": "Eccentricity < 0.05 — wareeg ku dhow goobaabin. Dhul (e=0.017) iyo Venus (e=0.007) halkan ayay ku nool yihiin.",
      "elliptical": "Ukun u eg",
