      "does_eccentricity_change_orbital_perio": "Eccentricity ma beddelaa MUDDADA wareegga? Isku day e=0 iyo e=0.5 isla a.",
      "halley_s_comet_has_a_17_8_au_e_0_97_wh": "Comet-ka Halley wuxuu leeyahay a=17.8 AU, e=0.97. Taasi maxay ka dhigan tahay muddadiisa — imisa jeerna perihelion ayuu booqdaa?",
      "if_the_sun_lost_half_its_mass_instantl": "Haddii Qorraxdu isla markiiba badhka cufkeeda lumiso, maxaa ku dhici lahaa muddada wareegga ee Dhulka?",
      "at_what_e_value_does_an_orbit_become_u": "Qiimaha e ee kee ayaa wareeg ka dhigaya mid aan xirnayn? Maxaa go'aamiya xadka?",
      "i_can_explain_why_this_a_e_m_combinati": "Waan sharxi karaa sababta isku-darka a/e/M uu u keenayo nooca wareeggan.",
      "explain_in_your_own_words": "Ku sharax erayadaada...",
      "inquiry_widget_no_score_no_reveal_no_a": "Widget baaritaan — dhibco ma jiraan, jawaab lama muujinayo, jawaab lama shubayo. T = √(a³/M) sida Kepler III, M cufka qorraxda, a AU, T sano. Vis-viva ayaa loo isticmaalaa v-ga perihelion / aphelion.",
      "full_orrery_animated_solar_system": "Orrery buuxa — nidaamka qorraxda oo dhaqaaqaya",
      "all_8_planets_to_scale_size_orbit_watc": "8-da planet oo dhan cabbir ahaan (weyni + wareeg). Daawo Mercury oo Qorraxda ku wareegaya ~4 jeer sanadkii Dhulka. Planet-yada gudaha way isku dhow yihiin; kuwa dibedda waxay maraan wareegyo waaweyn.",
      "kepler_i_orbits_are_ellipses": "Kepler I — wareegyadu waa ellipse",
      "every_planet_orbits_in_an_ellipse_with": "Planet kastaa wuxuu ku wareegaa ellipse Qorraxduna waxay ku taal hal focus. Focus-ka kale waa meel bannaan. Wareegga Dhulku aad buu u yar yahay janjeer ahaan (e ≈ 0.017).",
      "kepler_ii_equal_areas_in_equal_times": "Kepler II — bedad siman wakhtiyo siman",
      "a_line_from_planet_to_sun_sweeps_equal": "Xarriiq ka socota planet-ka ilaa Qorraxda waxay xaaqdaa bedad siman wakhtiyo siman — taasoo ka dhigan in planet-yadu ay DHAQSO u socdaan marka ay Qorraxda ku dhow yihiin (perihelion) ayna GAABIYAAN marka ay fog yihiin (aphelion).",
      "kepler_iii_period_semi_major_axis": "Kepler III — muddo² ∝ semi-major-axis³",
      "t_a_when_t_is_in_years_and_a_is_in_au_": "T² = a³ marka T uu sano yahay a-na AU yahay. Dhulka T=1, a=1 wuxuu xisaabta ka dhigayaa mid nadiif ah. Haddii aad cabbirka wareegga labanlaabto, muddadu waxay ku dhufan doontaa ~2.83.",
      "workshop_build_your_own_orbit": "Goobta shaqada — dhis wareeggaaga",
      "set_semi_major_axis_eccentricity_the_o": "Dhig dhidibka semi-major + eccentricity; orrery-gu wuxuu wareegga ku tusayaa wakhti dhab ah. Isku day e=0.9 — taasi waa meesha comet-yadu joogaan. Isku day e=0 — goobaabin sax ah.",
      "hohmann_transfers_actual_rocket_math": "Hohmann transfer — xisaabta dhabta ah ee gantaalka",
      "the_minimum_energy_way_to_travel_betwe": "Habka tamarta ugu yar ee lagu safro laba wareeg oo goobaabin ah dhexdooda. Laba gubasho: ka bax wareegga gudaha perihelion-ka transfer-ka, ku soo gaadh wareegga dibedda aphelion.",
      "challenges_apply_kepler_s_laws": "Caqabado — isticmaal sharciyada Kepler",
      "multi_step_problems_predict_periods_fr": "Dhibaatooyin tallaabo badan leh: saadaali muddooyinka dhidibka semi-major, garo xawaaraha perihelion iyo aphelion, xisaabi Δv-ga wareegga transfer-ka. Waa aagga AP Physics 1 + 2.",
      "true_false_concept_check": "Run / Been — eegis fikrad",
      "quick_discrimination_quiz_on_common_ke": "Su'aalo degdeg ah oo kala saara fikradaha qaldan ee caanka ah ee Kepler. Waxay bartilmaameedsanayaan been-abuurka wareegga (\"dhow = gaabis,\" \"wareegyadu waa goobaabin,\" \"wareegyada oo dhan isku jiho ayay u socdaan\").",
      "kepler_inquiry_orbital_mechanics_sandb_2": "Baaritaanka Kepler — goobta tijaabada orbital mechanics",
      "move_semi_major_axis_eccentricity_and_": "Dhaqaaji dhidibka semi-major, eccentricity, iyo cufka jirka dhexe. Saadaali nooca wareegga — goobaabin, ukun u eg, janjeersan, comet u eg, parabolic. Dhibco ma jiraan, jawaab lama muujinayo.",
