      "bigger_aperture_gathers_more_light_res": "Aperture weyn wuxuu iftiin badan ururiyaa + faahfaahin fiican muujiyaa. Magnification-ku wuu ka muhiimsanaan yaraa intaad u malaynayso.",
      "aperture_cm": "Aperture (cm)",
      "magnification": "Magnification",
      "aperture_matters_more_than_magnificati": "Aperture-ku wuu ka muhiimsan yahay magnification! Objective weyn wuxuu iftiin badan ururiyaa + faahfaahin fiican muujiyaa. Magnification ka badan qiyaastii 20x sentimitir kasta oo aperture ah wuxuu keliya khiyaano keenaa. Muraayadda 6.5 m ee JWST waxay baartaa galaxy-yo laga soo bilaabo boqollaal milyan sano ee ugu horreeyay Big Bang kadib.",
