      "altitude_2": "Joog",
      "phases_of_venus_galileo": "♀ Marxaladaha Venus (Galileo)",
      "galileo_s_1610_observations_venus_goes": "Waxa uu Galileo arkay 1610: Venus wuxuu maraa marxalado. Tani waxay caddaysay in Venus uu Qorraxda ku wareego, ee uusan Dhulka ku wareegin.",
      "earth_9": "Dhul",
