      "orbit_2": "Wareeg",
      "in_1610_galileo_observed_venus_through": "1610-kii Galileo wuxuu Venus ku eegay telescope-kiisa wuxuuna arkay inuu marxalado maro — sida Dayaxa. Tani waxay caddayn u ahayd in Venus uu Qorraxda ku wareego, ee uusan Dhulka ku wareegin. Nidaamka Ptolemy ee Dhulka dhexda dhiga ma sharxi karo Venus buuxa. Caddayn weyn oo taageeraysa heliocentrism-ka Copernicus.",
      "magnetic_field_visualizer": "🧲 Muujiyaha Beerta Birlabeed",
      "a_magnetic_field_deflects_solar_wind_p": "Beer birlabeed waxay iska celisaa dabaysha qorraxda + waxay ilaalisaa hawada. Mars labadaba wuu lumiyay; sidaas darteed wuu cidloobay.",
      "earth_10": "Dhul",
