      "solar_system_scale": "📐 Cabbirka Nidaamka Qorraxda",
      "switch_between_size_and_distance_views": "Beddel u dhexeeya aragtida cabbirka iyo tan masaafada. Labada isku mar cabbir dhab ah lagama tusi karo — sidaas ayuu bannaanku u yahay mid madhan.",
