      "true_scales_are_hard_to_show_simultane": "Cabbirrada dhabta ah isku mar way adag tahay in la tuso. Haddii Dhulku uu digir yahay, Qorraxdu waxay noqon lahayd kubbad badeed oo 200 fuudh u jirta. Haddii masaafooyinku cabbir dhab ahaadaan, planet-yadu waxay noqonayaan barro aan la arki karin. Sawirrada intooda badan way is-dhaafsadaan.",
      "lunar_lander_mini_game": "🛬 Ciyaarta Yar ee Degidda Dayaxa",
      "thrust_to_slow_your_descent_land_softe": "Isticmaal thrust si aad hoos u dhaca u gaabiso. Ka deg si ka jilicsan 2.5 m/s ama waad burburaysaa. Maamul shidaalka — kuma filna in aad si bilaash ah u taagnaato.",
