      "earth_12": "Dhul",
      "light_moves_300_000_km_s_we_see_distan": "Iftiinku wuxuu socdaa 300,000 km/s. Walxaha fog waxaan u aragnaa sidii ay ahaayeen markii iftiinku ka baxay. Qorraxda aan aragno waa 8 daqiiqo jir; Proxima Centauri waa 4 sano jir. Galaxy-ga Andromeda waa 2.5 milyan sano jir.",
      "sun_path_across_latitudes": "☀ Jidka Qorraxda ee Latitude-yada",
      "where_exactly_does_the_sun_rise_set_it": "Halkee ayay Qorraxdu ka soo baxdaa oo ay ku dhacdaa? Waxay ku xiran tahay latitude-kaaga + maalinta. Isku day Maine iyo Arctic Circle.",
      "latitude_2": "Latitude",
      "day_of_year": "Maalinta sanadka",
      "sun_path_depends_on_latitude_season_at": "Jidka Qorraxdu wuxuu ku xiran yahay latitude + xilliga. Dhexroorka, qorraxdu si toos ah ayay kor uga martaa. Arctic Circle, qorraxda habeenbadhka xagaaga solstice + habeen cidhifeed xilliga qaboobaha solstice. Portland ee Maine: xagaaga dhexdiisa qorraxdu way sarraysaa; jiilaalka dhexdiisa, qorraxdu ku dhawaad cirifka aragga ma dhaafto.",
      "habitable_moons": "🌙 Dayaxyada Lagu Noolaan Karo",
      "some_moons_may_host_life_europa_encela": "Dayaxyada qaar waxaa laga yaabaa inay nolol hayaan: Europa + Enceladus + Titan + Ganymede waxay leeyihiin badaha hoose. Hawlgallo firfircoon ayaa hadda raadinaya.",
      "europa_jupiter": "Europa (Jupiter)",
      "subsurface_ocean_has_2_water_of_earth_": "Badda hoose waxay leedahay 2× biyaha badaha Dhulka. Hydrothermal vent-yo ayaa suurtogal ah sagxadda badda. Hawlgallada JUICE + Europa Clipper way socdaan.",
      "enceladus_saturn": "Enceladus (Saturn)",
      "cassini_discovered_geysers_spraying_wa": "Cassini wuxuu helay ilo buufinaya biyo + organics + hydrogen + silica. Kiimikada uumiga waxay muujinaysaa walxaha + ilaha tamareed ee nolosha taageeri kara.",
      "titan_saturn": "Titan (Saturn)",
      "thick_atmosphere_of_n2_ch4_lakes_of_li": "Hawo qaro weyn oo N2 + CH4 ah. Harooyin methane dareere ah oo dusha ah. Bad biyo-ammonia ah oo hoose. Nolol waa suurtogal laakiin aad bay u duwan tahay.",
