      "expanding_ejecta_thousands_km_s": "Walxaha ballaadhaya: kumanaan km/s",
      "relative_brightness": "Dhalaal la barbardhigay",
      "wavelength_nm": "Wavelength (nm)",
      "key_visible_features": "Astaamaha muhiimka ah ee la arki karo: ",
      "spectral_line_strength_caution": "Xoogga xarriiqdu ma aha cabbir fudud oo badnaanta ah: heerkulka, culayska, iyo ionization-ka ayaa sidoo kale go'aamiya astaamaha ugu xoogga badan ee muuqda. Qalloocyadan waa moodelo waxbarasho oo la fududeeyay.",
      "spectra_life_paths_note": "Tusaalayaashani ma aha hal taariikh: xiddig Qorrax u eg wuxuu noqon karaa xiddig guduudan weyn iyo planetary nebula, halka supernova Nooca II uu dhammeeyo nolosha xiddig cuf weyn.",
      "time_zone_visualizer": "🕐 Muujiyaha Aagagga Wakhtiga",
      "earth_rotates_15_per_hour_watch_when_i": "Dhulku wuxuu wareegaa 15° saacaddii. Daawo marka ay duhur tahay Tokyo, iyo marka qorraxdu ka soo baxdo Portland.",
      "tokyo": "Tokyo",
      "beijing": "Beijing",
      "mumbai": "Mumbai",
      "cairo": "Cairo",
      "london": "London",
      "sao_paulo": "Sao Paulo",
