      "utc_hour": "Saacadda UTC",
      "earth_rotates_15_per_hour_utc_coordina": "Dhulku wuxuu wareegaa 15° saacaddii. UTC (Coordinated Universal Time) waa tixraaca caalamiga ah. Aagagga wakhtigu waxay ku kala duwan yihiin ±saacado. Portland Maine waa UTC-5 (EST) ama UTC-4 (EDT). Caalamka, badhka Dhulku waa iftiin halka badhka kalena uu habeen yahay.",
      "mind_blowing_facts_gallery": "💡 Bandhigga Xaqiiqooyinka Yaabka Leh",
