      "textbook_diagrams_lie_the_moon_is_much": "Sawirrada buugaagta waa been. Dayaxu wuu ka fog yahay sida loo sawiray. Eeg cabbirka dhabta ah.",
      "earth_15": "Dhul",
      "moon_4": "Dayax",
      "earth_16": "Dhul",
