      "most_textbooks_draw_the_moon_too_big_t": "Buugaagta intooda badan waxay Dayaxa u sawiraan mid aad u weyn + aad u dhow. Runta: dhexroorka Dayaxu waa 1/4 kan Dhulka, masaafada Dayaxuna waa ~30 dhexroor Dhul. Iftiinku wuxuu qaataa 1.3 ilbiriqsi safarka.",
      "day_length_comparison": "⏰ Isbarbardhigga Dhererka Maalinta",
