      "edwin_hubble_classified_galaxies_in_19": "Edwin Hubble wuxuu galaxy-yada kala saaray 1936 — \"Hubble tuning fork.\" Spiral-yo + elliptical-yo + irregular-yo. Galaxy-yadu waxay ku horumaraan isku-darsanaan — Milky Way wuxuu ku jiraa nolol-dhexe; isku-darsanaan Andromeda ah ayaa laga yaabaa inay bilyanaan sano gudahood timaaddo (daraasadaha 2025 waxay tirada dhigayaan ku dhow 50/50).",
      "cosmic_speeds_chart": "⚡ Shaxda Xawaarayaasha Koonka",
      "from_walking_to_light_speed_log_scale_": "Laga bilaabo socod ilaa xawaaraha iftiinka (cabbir log). Voyager 1 waa walaxda dadku sameeyeen ee ugu fog waana mid ka mid ah probe-yadeenna ugu dheereeya, laakiin weli koonka ahaan aad buu u gaabis yahay.",
      "voyager_1_is_the_fastest_object_humans": "Voyager 1 wuu dheereeyaa marka la eego dayax-gacmeedyada hadduna waa walaxda dadku sameeyeen ee ugu fog, haddana wuxuu weli qaadan lahaa qiyaastii 80,000 sano inuu xiddiga ugu dhow gaadho. Iftiinku isla safarkaas wuxuu ku dhammeeyaa 4 sano.",
      "star_forming_region": "✨ Goobta Samaynta Xiddigaha",
      "watch_stars_form_from_cold_dust_to_hot": "Daawo xiddigaha oo ka samaysmaya boodh qabow ilaa qorraxyo kulul. 6 marxaladood dhowr milyan sano gudahood.",
      "stars_are_born_in_clusters_from_giant_": "Xiddigaha waxaa lagu dhalaa kooxo ka soo jeeda daruuro molecular weyn. Nidaamka guud: dhowr milyan sano. Tusaalayaal caan ah: Orion Nebula (M42), Eagle Nebula (Pillars of Creation), Tarantula Nebula.",
      "big_cosmic_questions": "❓ Su'aalo Waaweyn oo Koonka ah",
      "10_of_the_deepest_open_questions_in_co": "10 ka mid ah su'aalaha furan ee ugu qoto dheer cosmology-ga. Qaar jawaab qayb ah ayay leeyihiin; qaarna waa qarsoodi kaliya.",
      "previous_3": "← Horr",
