      "solar_system_explorer_2": "Sahmiyaha Nidaamka Qorraxda",
      "40_interactive_mini_tools_svg_visualiz": "40+ qalab-yar oo la isticmaali karo, muuqaallo SVG ah, iyo simulation waxbarasho.",
      "from_a_moon_phase_dial_to_a_black_hole": "Laga bilaabo dial-ka marxaladaha dayaxa ilaa muujiyaha godka madoow ilaa pendulum-ka Foucault, qalab kasta waxaa loo dhisay in fikradaha aan taaban karin la dareemo + lagu ciyaaro.",
      "built_for_k_12_curious_adults_open_all": "Waxaa loo dhisay K-12 + dad waaweyn oo xiiseeya. Fur qalabka oo dhan, ama mid keliya — mid kastaa keligiis wuu shaqeeyaa.",
      "part_of_alloflow_stem_lab_built_in_mai": "Qayb ka mid ah AlloFlow STEM Lab. Waxaa lagu dhisay Maine, USA. Xogta oo dhan waxaa laga soo qaatay NASA, ESA, JAXA, USGS, IAU + ilo sayniseed oo dadweyne. Isticmaalka waxbarashadu waa bilaash.",
