      "best_naked_eye_observing_dark_site_awa": "Eegista ugu wanaagsan ee indhaha qaawan: meel madoow (nalalka magaalada ka fog), Dayaxu cirifka aragga ka hooseeyo, indhuhu la qabsadeen (20-30 daqiiqo mugdi). App bilaash ah: Stellarium, SkyView, Star Walk waxay ku caawiyaan inaad garato waxaad aragto.",
      "pale_blue_dot": "🌍 Bar Buluug ah oo Liita",
      "carl_sagan_s_most_quoted_reflection_a_": "Fikirka Carl Sagan ee ugu odhaah badan. Pixel ka kooban qof kasta oo aan waligeen naqaan.",
      "the_pale_blue_dot": "Barta Buluugga ah ee Liita",
      "from_this_distant_vantage_point_the_ea": "\"Meeshan fog laga eego, Dhulku wuxuu u muuqan karaa mid aan xiiso gaar ah lahayn. Laakiin annaga, way ka duwan tahay. Mar kale ka fikir bartaas. Taasi waa halkan. Taasi waa guriga. Taasi waa annaga. Korkeeda ayaa qof kasta oo aad jeceshahay, qof kasta oo aad taqaanno, qof kasta oo aad waligaa maqashay, bini'aadam kasta oo abid jiray, noloshooda ku noolaayeen.\"",
      "carl_sagan_pale_blue_dot_1994": "— Carl Sagan, Pale Blue Dot (1994)",
      "voyager_1_took_this_photo_of_earth_fro": "Voyager 1 wuxuu sawirkan Dhulka ka qaaday 6 bilyan km oo fog Feb 14, 1990 — codsi ka yimid Carl Sagan. Dhulku waa hal pixel. Bini'aadam kasta oo taariikhda jiray wuxuu ku noolaa pixel-kaas.",
