      "most_cities_have_one_members_lend_scop": "Magaalooyinka intooda badan mid bay leeyihiin. Xubnuhu telescope-yo way amaahiyaan, way baraan, xaflado xiddigo way qabtaan.",
      "dark_site": "Meel madoow",
      "drive_30_min_from_city_lights_maine_is": "Wad 30+ daqiiqo oo nalalka magaalada ka fog. Maine way ka buuxaan. Katahdin Woods and Waters waa hoy cir-madoobeed la xaqiijiyay.",
      "most_important_tool_dark_sky_light_pol": "Qalabka ugu muhiimsan: cir madoow. Wasakhda iftiinku waxay tirtirtaa 90% xiddigaha. Katahdin Woods and Waters NM iyo AMC Maine Woods waa goobo International Dark Sky ah oo la xaqiijiyay; Acadia iyo Baxter sidoo kale waxay leeyihiin cirar madoow oo aad u wanaagsan.",
      "how_stars_die": "⚱ Sida Xiddiguhu u Dhintaan",
      "star_s_fate_depends_on_mass_brown_dwar": "Aayaha xiddigu wuxuu ku xiran yahay cufka: brown dwarf, white dwarf, xiddig neutron ah, ama god madoow.",
      "how_a_star_dies_depends_almost_entirel": "Sida xiddig u dhinto ku dhowaad gebi ahaanba waxay ku xiran tahay cufkiisii hore. Xadka u dhexeeya xiddiga neutron-ka + godka madoow lama hubo (xadka Tolman-Oppenheimer-Volkoff ~2-3 M☉ ee hadhaaga).",
      "cosmic_distance_reference": "📏 Tixraaca Masaafada Koonka",
      "from_1km_to_93_billion_light_years_ref": "Laga bilaabo 1km ilaa 93 bilyan sano-iftiin. Shax tixraac ah oo cabbirrada koonka.",
      "distances_jump_in_scale_km_to_au_to_ly": "Masaafooyinku waxay cabbir ahaan boodaan: km ilaa AU ilaa ly ilaa bilyanaan ly. Tallaabo kastaa waa ~10,000-100,000× ka weyn. Cirbixiyeenimadu waxay ku nooshahay cabbir log ah.",
      "maine_night_sky_by_season": "🌲 Cirka Habeenkii ee Maine Xilli kasta",
      "maine_has_world_class_dark_skies_what_": "Maine waxay leedahay cirar madoow oo heer caalami ah. Waxa aad xilli kasta raadinayso.",
      "maine_has_fantastic_dark_skies_especia": "Maine waxay leedahay cirar madoow oo cajiib ah — gaar ahaan waqooyiga magaalooyinka. Katahdin Woods and Waters NM iyo AMC Maine Woods waa goobo International Dark Sky ah oo la xaqiijiyay; Acadia, Allagash, Baxter, iyo Cobscook sidoo kale aad bay u madoow yihiin. Habeennada jiilaalku way dheer yihiin + aad bay u saafi yihiin.",
      "space_news_timeline": "📰 Taariikhda Warka Bannaanka",
      "major_space_missions_events_2024_2027_": "Hawlgallo iyo dhacdooyin waaweyn oo bannaanka ah 2024-2027. Waxaan ku noolnahay wakhti xiiso leh.",
      "space_exploration_is_in_a_renaissance_": "Sahminta bannaanku waxay ku jirtaa soo noolayn. Waddammo cusub (Hindiya, Japan, UAE), shirkado gaar loo leeyahay oo cusub (SpaceX, Blue Origin), hawlgallo cusub (Europa Clipper, Artemis, JWST). Kor u eeg — oo fiiro gaar ah sii.",
      "solar_system_at_a_glance": "📊 Nidaamka Qorraxda Hal Aragti",
      "quick_reference_summary_of_solar_syste": "Soo koobid tixraac degdeg ah oo waxa nidaamka qorraxdu ka kooban yahay + qaybsanaanta cufka.",
      "solar_system_stats": "Tirakoobka Nidaamka Qorraxda",
      "the_sun_contains_99_86_of_all_solar_sy": "Qorraxdu waxay ku jirtaa 99.86% cufka nidaamka qorraxda oo dhan. Jupiter wuxuu qaataa laba meelood saddex meelood ee 0.14% hadhay. Dhulka + wax kastoo kale ayaa inta hadhay ah.",
