      "why_utc_matters": "🌐 Maxay UTC u Muhiim u Tahay",
      "astronomers_report_everything_in_utc_t": "Cirbixiyeennadu wax walba UTC ayay ku sheegaan. Sharraxaadda aagagga wakhtiga.",
      "why_we_use_utc": "Maxaan UTC u isticmaalnaa",
      "utc_coordinated_universal_time_is_the_": "UTC (Coordinated Universal Time) waa tixraaca caalamiga ah. Wuxuu ku salaysan yahay saacadaha atomka.",
      "astronomers_report_events_in_utc_so_ob": "Cirbixiyeennadu waxay dhacdooyinka ku sheegaan UTC si goobaha indho-indhaynta adduunka oo dhan ay isu barbardhigi karaan. SpaceX wuxuu ku duulaa UTC. Hawlgallada NASA waa UTC.",
      "maine_utc_5_est_or_utc_4_edt_london_ut": "Maine: UTC-5 (EST) ama UTC-4 (EDT). London: UTC+0 (GMT) ama UTC+1 (BST). Japan: UTC+9.",
      "tip_when_you_read_an_astronomy_event_t": "Talo: marka aad akhrido jadwal dhacdo cirbixiyeenimo, had iyo jeer hubi inuu UTC yahay mise mid deegaanka ah.",
      "utc_replaced_gmt_in_1972_based_on_atom": "UTC wuxuu beddelay GMT 1972. Wuxuu ku salaysan yahay saacadaha atomka ee shaybaadhyada qaranka ee adduunka oo dhan, oo celcelis loo qaaday. Ilbiriqsiyo boodis ah ayaa lagu daraa marka loo baahdo.",
