      "harmony": "Is-waafajin",
      "harmony_desc": "Baadh codadka isku raacsan iyo kuwa is diida, ku xir saamiyada frequency qaabka, oo u rog xiriirka muusigga mid muuqaal ah",
      "contrast": "Kala-duwanaan",
