      "educational_concepts": "💡 Fikrado Waxbarasho",
      "color_theory_additive_vs_subtractive_m": "Aragtida midabka (isku-dar lagu daro iyo mid laga jaro, midabbo is dhaafsan, HSL/RGB), xariiqyo qalloocan oo xisaabeed (hypotrochoids, Lissajous), fractals iyo is-ekaanshaha, joomatariga tessellation, sida indhuhu wax u arkaan ee op art, heerarka helitaanka WCAG, iyo farshaxan kombiyuutar. Qalab kasta wuxuu ku baraa xisaabta quruxda ka danbeysa.",
      "got_it_let_s_create": "Waan fahmay — aan abuurno! 🎨",
      "art_studio_sections": "Qeybaha Istuudiyaha Farshaxanka",
      "color_wheel_2": "Giraangirta Midabka",
