      "sculpt_3d": "Xardh 3D",
      "contrast_2": "Kala-duwanaan",
      "color_wheel_hsl_hsv_complementary_pair": "Giraangirta Midabka — HSL/HSV + lammaane is dhaafsan",
      "hue_0_360_around_the_wheel_saturation_": "Hue (0-360 giraangirta ku wareegsan), saturation (saafinta midabka), lightness (iftiinka). Kuwa is dhaafsan waa kuwa ka soo horjeeda, kuwa is dhow waa deriska, kuwa triadic waa 120° kala fog. Newton ayaa 1666 midabbada giraangir dul dhigay.",
      "color_mixer_subtractive_vs_additive": "Isku-darka Midabka — laga jaro iyo lagu daro",
      "paint_and_print_subtractive_cmy_mixes_": "Rinjiga iyo daabacaadda = laga jaro (CMY isku darkoodu wuxuu noqdaa madow); iftiinka iyo shaashadaha = lagu daro (RGB isku darkoodu wuxuu noqdaa cad). Adduun isku mid ah, laakiin xisaab gebi ahaanba kala duwan — daabacadu waxay ku fikirtaa plates K, telefishanku wuxuu ku fikiraa Hz.",
      "pixel_art_bitmap_craft_at_8_8_to_32_32": "Farshaxan Pixel — farsamada bitmap ee 8×8 ilaa 32×32",
      "each_pixel_is_a_deliberate_decision_ne": "Pixel kastaa waa go'aan la damacsan yahay. Sprites-ka NES waxay geesi ku qaadeen 8-nil 16×16 iyagoo isticmaalaya afar midab oo keliya. Algorithm-ka xariiqda ee Bresenham wuxuu sawiraa xariiq dhinac u jeeda isagoo aan tirooyin jajab ah isticmaalin.",
      "symmetry_reflection_rotation_glide": "Isku-ekaansho — muraayad, wareeg, iyo simbiriirixasho",
      "bilateral_mirror_rotational_n_fold_poi": "Labo dhinac (muraayad), wareeg (n-fold), iyo barta. 17-ka koox ee wallpaper waxay kala saaraan qaab kasta oo laba-cabbir ah oo isku celcelin leh — kaas oo ah shaqada Escher oo dhan.",
      "spirograph_hypotrochoid_roulettes": "Spirograph — roulettes hypotrochoid",
      "a_small_circle_rolls_inside_a_big_one_": "Goobo yar ayaa mid weyn gudihiis ku giringiraysa, qalinkuna wuxuu ka fogyahay bartamaha. Saamiga labada radius ayaa go'aamiya tirada ubaxyada; fogaanta qalinkuna waxay go'aamisaa dhumucda. Waxaa la naqshadeeyay 1965, laakiin xisaabtu waxay ka timid 1700-meeyadii.",
      "generative_algorithm_randomness_as_art": "Abuur — algorithm + kala-baxsad oo farshaxame ah",
      "sol_lewitt_wrote_instructions_the_wall": "Sol LeWitt wuxuu qoray tilmaamo keliya; ninkii derbiga ku shaqeeyay ayaa fuliyay. Maanta: Processing, p5.js, Cinder. “Farshaxamuhu waa xeerka, ma aha natiijada.”",
      "spin_art_centripetal_physics_in_paint": "Farshaxan Wareeg — fiisikiska bartame-u-jiidashada rinjiga",
      "drop_paint_spin_watch_it_fling_outward": "Rinji ku shub, wareeji, oo daawo sida uu dibadda ugu firdho wareegyo. Damien Hirst wuxuu malaayiin ka kasbaday iibinta sawirrada wareegga. Isla fiisikiska ka jira mashiinka ansalaatada; F = mω²r.",
      "string_art_curves_from_straight_lines": "Farshaxan Xarig — xariiqyo qalloocan oo ka yimid kuwo toosan",
      "connect_every_n_th_nail_an_envelope_cu": "Isku xir musmaar kasta oo N-aad ah; xariiq envelope ah ayaa soo baxaysa. Mary Everest Boole ayaa 1900 fasalka xisaabta ku soo bandhigtay. Cardioid-ka xariiqyada toosan ka samaysan wali indhaha wuu jiitaa.",
      "op_art_fooling_the_visual_system": "Op Art — khiyaamada nidaamka aragga",
      "bridget_riley_s_moir_fields_vasarely_s": "Goobooyinka moiré ee Bridget Riley, shabagyada Vasarely. Unugyada maskaxda ee dhaqdhaqaaqa ogaada ayaa xad-dhaafay marka kala-duwanaanshuhu si degdeg ah isu beddelo — bogguna wuxuu u muuqdaa mid *ruxmaya*.",
      "tessellation_the_17_wallpaper_groups": "Tessellation — 17-ka koox ee wallpaper",
      "every_periodic_2d_tiling_fits_one_of_1": "Tiling kasta oo laba-cabbir ah oo isku celcelin leh wuxuu ku dhacaa mid ka mid ah 17 koox oo isku-ekaansho ah. Escher wuxuu tan ogaaday markuu 1936 booqday Alhambra; kadibna 30 sano ayuu ku qaatay inuu dhammaystiro liiska.",
      "fractal_self_similar_at_every_scale": "Fractal — heer kasta isku eg",
      "mandelbrot_1975_cauliflower_coastlines": "Mandelbrot 1975. Kolifluur, xeebaha, xididdada dhiigga, hillaac, sambabbada — dhammaan waa fractal. “Daruuraha ma aha goobooyin, buurahana ma aha koonno, jiliftana ma aha mid siman.”",
      "gradient_smooth_color_transitions": "Gradient — isbeddel midab oo siman",
      "css_gives_you_linear_radial_and_conic_": "CSS wuxuu ku siiyaa gradient linear, radial, iyo conic. Qaansoroobaadka dhabta ahi wuxuu leeyahay midabbo isku xiran (ma jiraan qeybo kala go'an) — “7-da midab ee qaansoroobaadka” waxay ahayd doorasho Newton u sameeyay sabab muusiko awgeed.",
      "stereogram_3d_from_a_flat_page": "Stereogram — 3D oo bog siman ka soo baxaya",
      "90s_magic_eye_craze_each_eye_sees_a_sl": "Waalidii Magic Eye ee 90-meeyadii. Il kastaa waxay aragtaa sawir yar oo dhaqaaqay; haddaad indhaha si sax ah u isku dhawayso ama u kala fogayso, maskaxdu way isku darsataa oo qoto-dheer bay ka dhigtaa. Ilaa 5% dadka run ahaantii ma arki karaan — ma aha khaladkooda.",
      "contrast_wcag_4_5_1_3_1_apca": "Kala-duwanaan — WCAG 4.5:1 / 3:1 / APCA",
      "wcag_2_1_normal_text_4_5_1_large_3_1_w": "WCAG 2.1: qoraal caadi ah 4.5:1, mid weyn 3:1. Sababta kala-duwanaan yari u dhibto dadka aragga daciifka ah, xataa haddii adigu akhrisan kartid. APCA (kii ku xiga WCAG 3.0) wuxuu isticmaalaa iftiinka sida indhuhu u arkaan, ee ma aha saamiga luminance ee cad.",
      "harmony_lab_title": "Is-waafajin — cod, saami, iyo midab",
      "harmony_lab_hint": "Isbarbardhig codadka isku raacsan iyo kuwa is diida, ku xir saamiyada frequency qaabka, oo u rog xiriirka muusigga is-waafajin muuqaal ah.",
