      "adjust_base_hue_saturation_lightness_v": "Habee hue-ga aasaasiga ah, saturation, kala-duwanaanta iftiinka, wareegga, iyo cabbirka palette-ka. Widget-ku wuxuu tusayaa palette is-waafajin oo toos ah, wuxuuna u kala saaraa shan nooc oo is-waafajin ah. Dhibco ma jiraan, jawaab la kashifayo ma jirto — iska bedbeddel oo eeg isku-darka noocee is-waafajin keenaya.",
