      "some_color_schemes_have_proper_names_c": "Qorshayaal midab qaarkood magacyo gaar ah ayay leeyihiin (complementary, split-complementary, triadic). Raadi magacyadaas oo isku day inaad soo celisid.",
      "high_saturation_many_colors_busy_try_d": "Saturation sare + midabbo badan = mashquul. Isku day inaad saturation-ka ku yarayso slider-ka isku-darka — maxaa ku dhacaya \"is-waafajinta\"?",
      "i_think_i_understand_color_harmony_now": "Waxaan u malaynayaa inaan hadda fahmay is-waafajinta midabka — aan erayadeyda ku sharxo",
      "explain_in_your_own_words_how_do_hue_s": "Erayadaada ku sharax: sidee kala-fogaanta hue, saturation, iyo cabbirka palette-ka u go'aamiyaan \"is-waafajinta\"?",
      "design_note_discrete_5_state_harmony_m": "Xusuusin naqshadeed: calaamad is-waafajin oo shan xaaladood leh; giraangirta SVG waxay tusaysaa meelaha palette-ka; dhibco \"palette wanaagsan\" ma jiraan — sidaas ayaa loo qorsheeyay.",
