      "demand_slopes_down_cheap_buy_more_supp": "Qalooca baahidu wo hoos u janjeeraa (jaban = gado badan); qalooca sahaydu wo koor u janjeeraa (qaali = soo saar badan). Qiimaha iyo tirada dheelitirku waa halka ay isku tallaabaan. Buugga Adam Smith ee 1776, Wealth of Nations, wo weli yahay aasaaska.",
      "personal_finance_budgeting_saving_cred": "Maaliyad Shakhsi — miisaaniyad, kayd, amaah",
      "50_30_20_needs_wants_save_compound_int": "50/30/20: baahiyo / rabitaan / kayd. Dulsaarka isku-dhufanku waa yaabka siddeedaad; bilow 30 sano oo hore oo 7% ah wo u rogaa $1 $7.61. Kaararka amaahda si buuxda u bixi — 19% APR waa heer shabaq.",
      "stock_market_ownership_at_fractional_s": "Suuq Saami — lahaansho qeyb yar ah",
      "buy_a_share_own_a_slice_of_the_company": "Gado hal saami = waxaad leedahay qeyb ka mid ah shirkadda. S&P 500 wo bixiyay celcelis ~10% sanadkii muddo 100 sano ah. Kala firdhi (ha ku dhicin hal shirkad), muddo dheerna hay (waqti suuqa lagu joogo wo ka fiican in waqtiga la doonayo).",
      "business_sim_you_re_the_founder": "Jilitaan Ganacsi — adiga ayaa aasaasaha ah",
      "revenue_costs_profit_break_even_point_": "Dakhli − kharash = faayid. Barta dheelitirka kharashku waa marka kharashyada go'an ay daboolan yihiin. Ganacsiyada yaryar ee badankood wo ku dhacaan sanadka 5aad; kuwii badbaaday wo heleen alaab suuqu doonayo. Kharashka helitaanka macmiilka (CAC) iyo qiimaha nolosha macmiilka (LTV) waa xisaabta maalinlaha ah ee aasaasaha.",
      "national_economy_gdp_inflation_unemplo": "Dhaqaalaha Qaranka — GDP, qiim-koorid, shaqa-la'aan",
      "gdp_measures_total_output_cpi_measures": "GDP wo cabbiraa wadarta wax-soo-saarka; CPI wo cabbiraa qiim-koorid; shaqa-la'aanta U-3 waa heerka ugu weyn ee la sheego. Fed-ku wo dejiyaa heerarka dulsaarka si uu u dheelitiro kobac iyo qiim-koorid — labada waajib ee Congress-ku siiyay 1977.",
      "policy_inquiry_hero": "Baadhis Siyaasadeed — jawaab qarsoon ma jirto",
      "policy_inquiry_hero_hint": "Dhaqaaji jiidayaasha, saadaali xaalka makro KA HOR intaadan akhrin, kaddibna difaac fikirkaaga. Dhaqaaleyahannada dhabta ahi runtii wo isku khilaafaan calaamadahan iyo cabbirradan.",
      "try_supply_demand": "Tijaabi: dhig Xadka Qiimaha Koor $30 (xakameynta kirada). Marka hore saadaali — immisa xabbo ayuu suuqu ka yaraan doonaa?",
