      "as_price_quantity_demanded_consumers_b": "Marka qiimuhu ↑, tirada la baahan yahay ↓. Isticmaalayaashu wo yar gataan marka qiimuhu koro. Qalooca baahidu wo hoos u janjeeraa.",
