      "demand_shifted_left_fewer_people_want_": "▶ Baahidu wo u wareegtay BIDIX — Dad yar baa doonaya alaabtan (beddel baa raqiisay, ama doorbidku wo isbeddelay). Qiim IYO tiro labaduba wo hoos u dhacaan.",
      "supply_shifted_right_producers_can_mak": "▶ Sahaydu wo u wareegtay MIDIG — Soo-saarayaashu wo si raqiis ah wax badan u soo saari karaan (tignoolajiyad cusub, kharash alaab oo hoos u dhacay). Qiimuhu wo hoos u dhacaa, laakiin tiradu wo kortaa.",
      "supply_shifted_left_production_became_": "▶ Sahaydu wo u wareegtay BIDIX — Wax-soo-saarku wo adkaaday (masiibo dabiici ah, xeerar). Qiimuhu wo koraa, laakiin tiradu wo hoos u dhacdaa.",
